      "role": "user",
      "content": "i can't stop thinking about how nothing actually matters. like, if you look at the scale of everything, the universe is just expanding into nothingness and eventually everything just dies. so what's the point of even trying? all the struggle, the pain, the work... it's just a flash of light before total darkness. it feels like such a waste to even exist.",
